{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3>1.github 上创建 [username].github.io 工程</h3>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h3>2.检查是否有 Ruby，没有自行安装</h3>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;ruby&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>-</span><span>-</span></span><span>version</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h3>3.安装 Bundler</h3>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--require syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--special-method syntax--ruby\"><span>gem</span></span><span>&nbsp;install&nbsp;bundler</span></span></span></div></pre></div>\n<!--more-->\n<p>如果遇到无法安装的情况，需要添加其他资源，推荐淘宝的。</p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--require syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--special-method syntax--ruby\"><span>gem</span></span><span>&nbsp;sources&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>-</span></span><span>l</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--require syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--special-method syntax--ruby\"><span>gem</span></span><span>&nbsp;sources&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>-</span><span>-</span></span><span>remove&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--other syntax--symbol syntax--hashkey syntax--ruby\"><span>https</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--constant syntax--ruby\"><span>:</span></span></span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>/</span><span>/</span></span><span>rubygems</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--separator syntax--method syntax--ruby\"><span>.</span></span><span>org</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--require syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--special-method syntax--ruby\"><span>gem</span></span><span>&nbsp;sources&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>-</span></span><span>a&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--other syntax--symbol syntax--hashkey syntax--ruby\"><span>https</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--constant syntax--ruby\"><span>:</span></span></span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>/</span><span>/</span></span><span>ruby</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--separator syntax--method syntax--ruby\"><span>.</span></span><span>taobao</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--separator syntax--method syntax--ruby\"><span>.</span></span><span>org</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--require syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--special-method syntax--ruby\"><span>gem</span></span><span>&nbsp;sources&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>-</span></span><span>l</span></span></span></div></pre></div>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h3>4.安装 Jekyll</h3>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;sudo&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--require syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--special-method syntax--ruby\"><span>gem</span></span><span>&nbsp;install&nbsp;github</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>-</span></span><span>pages</span></span></span></div></pre></div>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h3>5.进入本地 [username].github.io 工程，创建 Gemfile 文件，添加</h3>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--meta syntax--require syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--other syntax--special-method syntax--ruby\"><span>gem</span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--string syntax--quoted syntax--single syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--begin syntax--ruby\"><span>&#39;</span></span><span>github-pages</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--string syntax--end syntax--ruby\"><span>&#39;</span></span></span></span></span></div></pre></div>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h3>6.运行 jekyll 查看效果</h3>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;bundle&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--support syntax--function syntax--kernel syntax--ruby\"><span>exec</span></span><span>&nbsp;jekyll&nbsp;serve&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--keyword syntax--operator syntax--arithmetic syntax--ruby\"><span>-</span><span>-</span></span><span>watch</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<p>添加 --watch 能即使看到文件的变化<br/>\n浏览器访问 <a href=\"http://localhost:4000\">http://localhost:4000</a> 可以访问当前目录 index.html 文件</p>\n<hr>","frontmatter":{"path":"/UOPviWrgplyuzTXh7jQZxSHl","title":"基于 Jekyll 搭建 github 博客","date":"2015-05-11 12:24:38 +0800","comments":true,"categories":"programming","author":"Sir0xb","tags":["github","jekyll"]}}},"pageContext":{}}